{"tid":482604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［慈母］掃地阿嬸憑慳儉儲550萬助兒子上車","createTime":"2017-11-28T10:16:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-28T12:45:40.000Z","uid":39539,"like":51,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"684603312a394a85e0d6fae1807cac8ee4a3e236","tid":482604,"uid":39539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T10:16:42.000Z","msg":"新界指標上車盤沙田第一城樓價直逼千一萬，市場消息指出，沙田第一城6座中層D室，實用面積853方呎，以1,095萬元售出，實用呎價12,837元。 <br />\n<br />\n上址售價打破屋苑一個面積相同的連天台單位去年錄得的1,080萬元紀錄，創屋苑做價史上新高。據了解，單位同時獲3組買家爭購，終於由一名買家以1,095萬元奪得，更代業主支付代理佣金搶贏。 <br />\n<br />\n市場消息指出，沙田第一城新樓王買家為一名約50多歲的清潔女工，居於沙田第一城附近的居屋屋苑，另在沙田河畔區持有另一個細單位收租，是次協助其約25歲兒子置業，並支付樓價一半即約550萬元作為首期。"},{"pid":"c45c8dd1c37999c779272bdf964d8a4aa4f2b4e2","tid":482604,"uid":26451,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T10:17:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"35538eaeb61015a668ae5bc86c0dbd808a2b1d65","tid":482604,"uid":1895,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score":48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T10:18:25.000Z","msg":"癡撚線 掃地除左自己住個到 仲有個細單位收租 仲可以比550萬首期？"},{"pid":"91cc52b7a9ee83ab2427b3e220ed48c959a4bd70","tid":482604,"uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T10:19:37.000Z","msg":"清潔工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"763b3600ff0100ee50a5ca599ddca04389308958","tid":482604,"uid":19552,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T10:20:37.000Z","msg":"個仔25歲孭到500萬按揭 收入都幾勁"},{"pid":"6bb3fe76dda9d1f3e54708ceb9c1177d6a5a36e4","tid":482604,"uid":116530,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T10:20:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddeb0629b4dcaa3bd50827aa11ff1a7d6fabf237","tid":482604,"uid":61105,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T10:22:58.000Z","msg":"人地掃地係興趣黎咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b40a5347163a9d3518301ef4e82386500329f7f5","tid":482